{
  "text": "For the restricted class of supertranslation generators P a,b with both (a, b) > −1, condition (8.7) was also proposed in [CITATION_1] . With this definition of the primary state the BMS descendants are given by,",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "118417893"
